quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  111,1,Perish the hands of the Father of Flame (Abu’-Lahab)! Perish he
  111,2,"(There is) no benefit to him (in the Hereafter) from all his wealth, and from all his gains"
  111,3,Soon he will be burnt in a Fire of burning Flame
  111,4,"And his wife shall carry the (crackling) wood, as fuel"
  111,5,A twisted rope of palm-leaf fiber around her (own) neck